Package eu.df.jiffybox.models

Class Plan

java.lang.Object
eu.df.jiffybox.models.Plan
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable<Plan>
public class Plan
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<Plan>
A plan consists of an id, a name, a disk size in MB, a RAM in MB, a price per hour, a price per hour frozen and the number of CPUs.
